name: DMT Goddess beacons you... "Dance with me."
description:
Published in Prosthetic Reality v2, the first Augmented Reality NFT artbook. For more pieces in the collection follow the god of neon artwork, @Sutu on Twitter. 

Those who purchase this NFT can request a HIGH RES PRINT FILE: 19660 x 14948. The static artwork up 50" which can be used to trigger the augmented reality animation. A QR code will also be included for AR activation for anyone who requests it @garretthoyos on Twitter. Proof of ownership is required.

This artwork can be viewed as Augmented Reality with this link: https://launch.eyejackapp.com/Artwork-2ca4ad98-9d4c-4697-998e-87b5d6928581

If you scan the book or my artwork with your Eyejack app you can watch it come to life through your camera app on your phone, or AR glasses in the future.

Created using Quill / Character Creator / Nvidia Omniverse / After Effects / Eyejack Creator on a NVIDIA RTX3090. 

DMT Goddess beacons you "Dance with Me" was inspired by my journey of 11 years of CGI creative work, and 4 years of diving deep into human consciousness.
